                <h2>3. Kyoto, Japan—Confluence of Tradition and Calm</h2>
                <p>Pleasant are those who find the convergence of deep history and serene beauty and have the experience that makes this city so special.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The old temples, lovely gardens, and magnificent shrines speak to Kyoto as really the cultural heart of Japan. </li>
