                <h2>4. Marrakech, Morocco—A Colorful Journey Into the Heartland of Africa</h2>
                <p>This city is all about ancient traditions combined with modern influences in a pleasantly busy atmosphere.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The riot of colours, smells of spices, and the touch of handmade crafts in the mouthwatering souks of the Medina assail the senses. </li>
