                <h2>7. Bali, Indonesia: The Beaches Inspired by Sunrays</h2>
                <p>This island in the tropics has always been a top-of-the-line destination for travellers seeking sunny holidays.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>It is graced with beautiful beaches, wonderful rice terraces, and famous columns of arts-it has something for everyone. </li>
