                    <li>This safari haven has a breathtaking landscape and, of course, the Great Migration, which is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to experience the Big Five lions, leopards, elephants, buffaloes, and rhinos in their natural environment within the majestic curves of this savannah. </li>
